title: VTJ Karlovy Vary
text:
VTJ Karlovy Vary was a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club in <a href="Karlovy%20Vary">Karlovy Vary</a>, <a href="Czech%20Republic">Czech Republic</a>.
In 1995 the club was incorporated into <a href="FC%20Slavia%20Karlovy%20Vary">SK Slavia Karlovy Vary</a>. Its last placement was 13th in the <a href="1994%E2%80%9395%20Bohemian%20Football%20League">1994–95</a> <a href="Bohemian%20Football%20League">Bohemian Football League</a>.
